          <div class="sp_inner_content introduction_inner_content">
            <div class="sp_main_header">introduction</div>
            <p>The first paid Spefz event we intend to promote is located at <span class="">Brasserie Blanc (Bank), 60 threadneedle street, london, United Kingdom, EC2R 8HP</span> on the <span class="">28th of June 2018</span>. <span>Link to view event >> <%= link_to "Speed Social - Elite Professionals", "https://www.spefz.com/events/speed-social-elite-professionals/preview", target:"_blank", class: "content_link" %></span></p>
            <p>Spefz is a selective social dating app that holds exclusive live events for our registered members on the platform. Our current community of followers are between the ages of 28-48. We create profiled live events that gather and group individuals of similar interests and preferences, so the probability of members connecting will be much higher; we do this by auto-matching individuals to specific events (via our internal rating algorithm system on personality, physical appearance and interests) in order to ensure our members are able to network effectively and meet like-minded people of their calibre.</p>
            <p>We aim to create events that offer busy professionals a great way to meet new people in a fun, safe and chilled environment. The main key to creating our events is based on our internal algorithm that ensures that the compatibility and mutual interests of our members are met.</p>
            <p><b>Our Mission:</b> Our goal is to ensure that the compatibility and mutual interests of our members are met via our events and by subscribing to our online platform to help them to find their potential life partner.</p>
            <p><b>Our Vision:</b> Our vision is to help 1,000s of Londoners to find their ‘potential’ life partner. We use an algorithmic rating system based on personality, physical appearance and interests to auto-match individuals to specific events in order to ensure our members are able to network effectively and meet like-minded people of their caliber.</p>
