            <li>
              <span>Creating events for our members in the best UK's most stylish venues. Events are held on a weekly bases.</span>
              <div>There 3 main types of events Spefz organizes:</div>
              <ul>
                <li>
                  <u>SpeedDating Events:</u>
                  <div>maximum number of attendees 40. This is a seated event. Women are seated and men circulate. 5 mins given to each member to communicate with one another.</div>
                </li>
                <li>
                  <u>MixMatch Events:</u>
                  <div>maximum number of attendees 60. This is both a seated and standing networking event. Spefz team take the initiative in introducing members to one another based on algorithm stats created on the web platform.</div>
                </li>
                <li>
                  <u>Socials/After-work Drinks:</u>
                  <div>maximum number of attendees 30. These are socials, after work drinks/meeting, where subscribed members can attend.</div>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </li>
