            <p>Since early 2017, Spefz Ltd has been aiming to focus on helping its members effectively meet, network and connect with ambitious, like-minded people of their calibre through social dating & networking events. Our Team and Webapp platform brings and contributes a wealth of knowledge and experience that is unmatched in the event dating/networking industry.</p>
            <p>
              <b>Why We Do What We Do</b><br/>
              <span>We are passionate about connecting the right people via live events. We believe these days a lot of social dating & networking events are focused mainly on gathering random individuals to an event. We would like to be a part of changing that by gathering individuals of similar interests and personality traits at an event, thus increasing the likely hood of members being connected with other members of their calibre and preference.</span>
            </p>
            <p>
              <b>The Event Leadership Team</b><br/>
