            <div class="sp_main_header">problem statement</div>
            <p>
              <b>What problem are we solving?</b><br/>
              <span>Our research suggests that, while there is a number of specialist dating events based on ethnicity, culture, religion, sex-orientation, age, professionals etc, most of these specialist-dating events do not analyze their matches for their live dating events. They host their live dating events based on grouping people but not based on a match analyses on interest, preferences, personality and appearance, rather than focusing on gethering a set of people of the same physical attraction & personality. This results in the increased probability of unsuccessful matches between members at live dating events. </span>
            </p>
            <p>To ensure real people are able to meet like-minded singles, we've created a algorithm rating system on appearance and personality. This ensures that compatibility and mutual interests prevail. Does this take time? Yes. Is it worth it? Absolutely!</p>
            <div class="page_number_section">
