        <!-- proposedsolution_content -->
        <div class="medium-12 columns businessproposal_content proposedsolution_content">
          <div class="sp_inner_content value_inner_content">
            <div class="sp_main_header">proposed solution</div>
            <p><b>How do we solve the problem?</b><br/>
            <span>To ensure real people are able to meet like-minded singles we have an inbuilt algorithm rating and matching system for our live dating events. This algorithm automatically calculates the average rating of each member, uses this average rating to auto-match each member to a specific live dating event (where members with similar average rating score will be present). Our Spefz Team then also takes advantage of the available stats on each member and takes the initiative to introduce members with very close rating scores with one another. The introduction and automated process ensures members are able to meet and connect with like-minded singles and therefore increasing the likelihood of successful matches at each event.</span></p>
            <div class="page_number_section">
