            </p>
            <p><b>Why will customers buy this business’ services instead of your competitor?</b><br/>
            <span>We believe our inbuilt rating algorithm will attract users to attend our events – which most of our competitors do not have – Most of our competitors focus more on gathering random singles who are willing to pay to attend an event. We want to gather and group singles of similar interest, so the potential of members connecting will be much higher. We believe our users are likely to attend our events as we auto-match individuals to specific events (via our internal rating algorithm system based on personality, physical appearance and interests) in order to ensure they are able to network effectively and meet like-minded people of their calibre.</span></p>
            <div class="page_number_section">
