            <div class="sp_main_header">summary</div>
            <p>We believe that our online events dating platform service could do amazingly well. We believe our inbuilt rating algorithm will attract users to attend our events – which most of our competitors do not have – Most of our competitors focus more on gathering random singles who are willing to pay to attend an event. We want to gather and group singles of similar interest, so the potential of members connecting will be much higher. We believe our users are likely to attend our events as we auto-match individuals to specific events (via our internal rating algorithm system based on personality, physical appearance and interests) in order to ensure they are able to network effectively and meet like-minded people of their calibre.</p>
            <p>With my few years of experience in the event sector, i have seen this gap in the online events dating market, and I believe an online dating events platform that calculates a members stats and screens through each member in order to increase the probability of successful matches at live dating events is much needed. Using my skills, and experience in this space, I believe that I can turn this business into a great success and commercialise this platform to generate sustainable turnover and profitability.</p>
